Interface UncombinableCircuitModifier

All Superinterfaces:
CircuitModifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
Measurement
public non-sealed interface UncombinableCircuitModifier extends CircuitModifier
The UncombinableCircuitModifier interface extends CircuitModifier and represents a circuit modifier that cannot be combined with other circuit modifiers for optimization. Implementing classes must define specific modifications that cannot be simplified or combined with other modifiers.
